2
00:00:02,480 --> 00:00:04,070
Stella!

3
00:00:04,070 --> 00:00:05,780
Are you there?

4
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:09,570
Dear me...

5
00:00:09,950 --> 00:00:11,910
They sure caused a lot of damage.

6
00:00:12,410 --> 00:00:17,540
Even though they were born here,
the seraphim didn't hold back...

7
00:00:26,170 --> 00:00:27,220
An explosion?!

8
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:29,010
Come in!

9
00:00:29,010 --> 00:00:30,390
What was that explosion?

10
00:00:30,890 --> 00:00:32,510
Are you okay, Pythagoras?!

11
00:00:33,140 --> 00:00:34,350
Come in!

12
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:36,180
Pythagoras!

13
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:37,980
Answer me!

14
00:00:38,350 --> 00:00:39,810
What happened?!

15
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:16,030
LABOPHASE DEATH GAME

16
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:19,990
Building C, camsnail 12, scan the area.

17
00:02:20,370 --> 00:02:22,210
Find Pythagoras!

18
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:25,250
Was it an accident?

19
00:02:25,250 --> 00:02:26,960
I hope he wasn't caught in it...

20
00:02:31,670 --> 00:02:32,880
I just saw something!

21
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,430
A figure?!

22
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,600
Hey!

23
00:02:43,350 --> 00:02:45,480
The camsnail was destroyed...

24
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:48,520
What's wrong, Luffy?

25
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,610
This thing is broken.

26
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,110
Where are you going?

27
00:02:53,110 --> 00:02:55,820
I'm gonna go see Helmet for a bit.

28
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,990
Building C

29
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,990
Building B

30
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,990
Building A

31
00:02:57,990 --> 00:02:58,030
Building C

32
00:02:57,990 --> 00:02:58,030
Building B

33
00:02:57,990 --> 00:02:58,030
Building A

34
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:58,070
Building C

35
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:58,070
Building B

36
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:58,070
Building A

37
00:02:58,070 --> 00:02:58,120
Building C

38
00:02:58,070 --> 00:02:58,120
Building B

39
00:02:58,070 --> 00:03:03,080
Third Floor
Building A

40
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,160
Building C

41
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,160
Building B

42
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:58,200
Building C

43
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:58,200
Building B

44
